ing: 1 (14.5 ounce) can whole berry cranberry sauce
des: "This is a delicious and easy way to prepare chicken breasts.  I like to serve the cooked sauce over mashed potatoes or rice."
ins:
Place the chicken breasts in the bottom of a slow cooker. Pour the salad dressing, cranberry sauce, and onion soup mix over the chicken.
Cook on Low 4 to 6 hours.
